### ==== FORMS API ====
# Docs: http://localhost:5000/scalar/v1
# Base routes:
#   /api/v1/forms/templates    — form template CRUD + publish lifecycle (Admin)
#   /api/v1/forms/submissions  — form submission + query (Authenticated)
#
# Template lifecycle: Draft (inactive) → Published (active, accepts submissions)

# ── Form Templates ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List active form templates for a tenant (paged)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/forms/templates?tenantId={{tenantId}}&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get single form template schema by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/forms/templates/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create form template (starts inactive — requires publish before accepting submissions)
# Admin/SystemAdmin only
# SchemaJson: JSON Schema string defining the form fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/forms/templates
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "name": "Land Dispute Application Form",
  "nameVi": "Mẫu Đơn Khiếu Nại Đất Đai",
  "schemaJson": "{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"plotNumber\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"title\":\"Số thửa đất\"},\"area\":{\"type\":\"number\",\"title\":\"Diện tích (m²)\"},\"notes\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"title\":\"Ghi chú\"}},\"required\":[\"plotNumber\",\"area\"]}",
  "createdBy": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

###

### Publish form template (makes it active for submissions)
# Admin/SystemAdmin only
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/forms/templates/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "updatedBy": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

# ── Form Submissions ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Submit data against an active form template
# Data: key-value map matching the template's JSON Schema properties
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/forms/submissions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "formTemplateId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "submittedBy": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "data": {
    "plotNumber": "123",
    "area": "500",
    "notes": "Adjacent to main road, disputed boundary on north side."
  }
}

###

### Get single form submission by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/forms/submissions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List submissions filtered by template (paged)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/forms/submissions?tenantId={{tenantId}}&templateId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List all submissions for a tenant (no template filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/forms/submissions?tenantId={{tenantId}}&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
